overview: Following a one year timeskip, a lot has changed in the realm of the Cinephiles, new members have been added and dirt has been undig. It's become apparent that one of the OG Cinephiles had been duping the rest from the start. A conniving pedophilic ginger going under the pseudoname "Thomas" had been the strings and manipulating the innocent e-girls the entire time. How could any of them seen this coming? The answer may shock you. This film will delve deeper into the enigma that is "Seth Tward" as more of the story comes to fruition.
tagline: HOW ONE MAN TRICKED THE WORLD
title: Cinephiles 3 .
